title: 8 Pin 0.156 Header with crimp pins - 3.96 pitch
blurb:
The contacts are rated at 250V @ 7A AC/DC which makes them an ideal power connector to a PCB. They are end to end stackable and commonly seen as the output connector on Switchmode power supplies.
- Wire Pull- Out force: 2.85kg
- Unmating Force: 150g
- Durability: 25 cycles
- Housing: Nylon, UL 94V- 2
- Temperature: - 40 to 105°C
